  "texts": [
    "Typically, these models are validated using a subset of data from the entire dataset.",
    "Although a model may exhibit a perfect accuracy of 100% for this specific subset, it doesn't assure a similar level of performance for the entire continuous region of operation.",
    "Practically speaking, testing an ML model across the entirety of this continuous region is not feasible, given the infinite number of data points it encompasses.",
    "This adds another layer of complexity to the problem, presenting the need to develop a robust method that can validate the model's performance across the entire operating region, rather than just a data subset.",
    "The scarcity of high-quality data in the power system sector presents a formidable challenge when developing data driven technics."
  ],
